<varlistentry id="options.Resize">
	<term>Resize <emphasis remap='I'>"mode"</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Tells Animate what method to use to draw resizes.  The six meth-
              ods currently supported are: zoom,  zoom3D,  twist,  flip,  turn
              and random.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="AnimateTypes#synopsis">Animate Resize type</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
